\[
p(x)=-1.53426+2.18223 x-0.761675 x^{2}+0.113706 x^{3} .
\]

Using instead the general algorithm given on the previous page yields the alternative representation

\[
p(x)=(x-1)-.30685(x-1)^{2}+.113706(x-1)^{2}(x-2) .
